name: the Evening
description: Oil painting created by artist Benicio Gaudino, inspired by the moments. Digitally transformed (1010x666 pixels) - www.beniciogaudino.art. Those who buy the NFT will be drawn to the real Screen, in frame. Inspiration: No matter how hard our day has been, there’s no way you can’t help but smile when you see a sunset gracing the sky and lighting us up. The heart fills with gratitude as we observe that landscape and realize that nature surprises us every day. This phenomenon brings a lot of peace to our hearts and is always a spectacle to be admired.
